## Demisto Content Release Notes for version 19.5.1 (1)
##### Published on 02 June 2019
### Integrations

####  3 New Integrations
- __Ipstack__
One of the leading IP to geolocation 
APIs and global IP database services worldwide.

.
- __Looker__
Use the Looker integration to query an explore, save queries as looks, run looks, and fetch look results as incidents.
- __Palo Alto Networks PAN-OS__
Manage Palo Alto Networks Firewalls and Panorama. Make sure you read the Detailed Instructions section.

####  2 Improved Integrations
- __Palo Alto Networks WildFire v2__
return wildfire-report as pdf file.
- __FortiGate__
Added enhancement to update-policy, enabled keeping the existing data.

##### Removed Integrations
- __Panorama__

---
### Scripts

####  2 Improved Scripts
- __CommonServerPython__
Camelize support for Python3. Fixed bug in Camelize function.
- __IncidentAddSystem__
Added a new engine argument.

---
### Playbooks

####  2 Improved Playbooks
- __WildFire - Detonate file__
Enable using WildFire and WildFire-v2 integrations to run the playbook.
- __Extract Indicators From File - Generic__
Fixed mistaken identification of excel files as word documents.
